agonscale False Allegiance|1Dragonscale Vigilance	NAMEISPI:YES	KEY:Dragonscale Loyalist ~ Dragonscale Vigilance		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Feature.DragonscaleLoyalistClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																DESCISPI:YES	SOURCEPAGE:p.25	DESC:A Dragonscale loyalist becomes supernaturally perceptive to plots against his lord. While in his vigilante identity, a Dragonscale loyalist is treated as constantly being under the effects of the perceive betrayal spell. This effect’s caster level is equal to the Dragonscale loyalist’s vigilante level, and he doesn’t require material components or a focus.Conqueror's Wrath					KEY:Dragonscale Loyalist ~ Conqueror's Wrath			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Feature.DragonscaleLoyalistClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary															DESCISPI:YES	SOURCEPAGE:p.25	DESC:Inspired by the deeds of Choral the Conqueror, a loyalist can rampage through enemy ranks. As a full-round action, a Dragonscale loyalist can make a full attack and move up to his speed. The loyalist can pause at any point or points during the movement, make one or more of his attacks, and continue moving. Creatures making attacks of opportunity against the loyalist during this movement gain a +4 bonus on their attack and damage rolls. Using this ability counts as using a vigilante talent.House Garess		NAMEISPI:YES	KEY:False Allegiance ~ House Garess					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:FalseAllegiance.SpecialQuality																									DESCISPI:YES	SOURCEPAGE:p.24	DESC:The Dragonscale loyalist gains Sure Grasp and dwarves’ stonecunning racial trait.																										ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Sure Grasp					ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Dwarf ~ StonecunningHouse Lebeda		NAMEISPI:YES	KEY:False Allegiance ~ House Lebeda					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:FalseAllegiance.SpecialQuality																									DESCISPI:YES	SOURCEPAGE:p.24	DESC:The Dragonscale loyalist gains Skill Focus (Appraise). He can 